com.aventstack.extentreports.reporter

Class ExtentKlovReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aventstack.extentreports.reporter.ConfigurableReporter
      • com.aventstack.extentreports.reporter.AbstractReporter
        • com.aventstack.extentreports.reporter.ExtentKlovReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnalysisStrategyService, ExtentReporter, TestListener

    public class ExtentKlovReporter
extends AbstractReporter
    ExtentKlovReporter is a NoSQL database reporter (MongoDB), which updates information in the database which is then used by the ExtentX server to display in-depth analysis.
